        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 9020 Rasor Boulevard, Plano, TX 75024 Whether you’re in northeastern Texas for work, a family visit, or an unexpected stay, you can settle right in at ECHO Suites Extended Stay by Wyndham Dallas Plano/Frisco. Each of our thoughtfully designed suites features everyday essentials—from kitchens with cooktops and full-size refrigerators to free standard WiFi and smart TVs with streaming and casting. We’re happy to be your home away from home in Plano with an on-site fitness center and convenient laundry facilities. Plus, you can bring your dog along for the duration of your stay with dog-friendly suites (additional fees apply). Situated off Sam Rayburn Tollway and Dallas North Tollway, our north Dallas extended-stay hotel offers easy access to both the Plano and Frisco downtown areas, Medical City Plano Hospital, Comerica Center, and Toyota Stadium. Features Include: Mobile Check-in EV Charging Early Check-in Available Accessible Route to Accessible Guestrooms Digital Room Key 100% Smoke-Free Hotel Accessible Front Desk Business Center Free WiFi Pet Friendly 24-Hour Front Desk Express Check-out Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livegulfcoasthm.com/cotlqvwe/echo-suites-extended-stay-by-wyndham-dallas-plano- We allow up to two dogs (maximum 35 lbs. each) per room for a fee of $50 for the first night and $10 per pet, per night thereafter.",
