        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to The Glen at Highpoint! The key to our apartments on Markville Dr. in North Dallas is their coveted location, brimming with live-work-play opportunities and luxury. Find your happy place and discover our thoughtfully designed floor plans, complete with premium finishes. Enter our apartments for rent in North Dallas, presenting generous one and two-bedroom layouts with balconies and patios, which expand your space even more. They feature exceptional living quarters and lavish finishes to meet your needs. The fully-equipped kitchens will turn each meal into an experience, and the window coverings will offer you privacy on the days you need it. In addition, select units feature vaulted ceilings, extra storage space, and sunrooms. Contact us to schedule a personal tour with one of our friendly and professional staff members today! -Short Term Lease -3 Naturally Designed Swimming Pools -On-Site Maintenance -Carport -Flex Rent -Social Lounge -$0 Deposit -Clubhouse -Naturally Designed Outdoor Hot Tub -Laundry Facilities -Business Center -Playground Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livepriderock.com/tjiclvlo/glen-at-highpoint Pricing and availability are subject to change. Contact leasing office for details.",
