        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  1 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  1036 Date Available:  2026-06-19 Address:  3701 N O'Connor Rd Las Colinas Heights Apartments offers stylish 1- and 2-bedroom floor plans in the heart of the prestigious Las Colinas neighborhood. Located near iconic attractions like the Las Colinas Country Club, Las Colinas Convention Center, Toyota Music Factory, Mandalay Canal Walk, and Irving Arts Center, our community blends luxury and convenience seamlessly. Our modern apartments feature cozy fireplaces, private patios or balconies, walk-in closets, and efficient appliances, creating the perfect space to relax and unwind. Enjoy premium amenities such as a resort-style swimming pool, a 24-hour fitness center, and a serene courtyard, all designed to enhance your lifestyle. Ideal for professionals, Las Colinas Heights provides easy access to major employers and highways, including Highway 114 and the George Bush Turnpike, ensuring your commute is a breeze. Elevate your living experience by making Las Colinas Heights your new home. Schedule a tour and discover firsthand the exceptional living that awaits you in Irving, TX. This community complies with the requirements of Texas Local Government Code § 394.9026(c)(7). All applicants are subject to standard screening criteria and program requirements. Housing Choice Voucher applicants are welcome to apply! Amenities Include: Disability Access On-site Professional Management Mini Blinds Loft Zero Deposit Community Business Center Walk-in Closets State of the Art Fitness Center 9-foot Ceilings Refrigerator Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewithtopaz.com/e72kixb3/las-colinas-heights Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
