        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 1455 N. Perry Rd, Carrollton, TX 75006 Bedrooms:  1 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  652 Rent Price:  1105 Sevilla Condos is surrounded by mature oak trees that whisk you away from the noise of a busy day while still being conveniently located minutes from Carrolltons Historic Downtown. Still holding on to its old world charm, Carrollton has been expanding with many new restaurants and shops making this a premiere location for the Dallas-Fort Worth area. Tie that into the easy access to major highways such as the President George Bush Tollway, 35E, and 635; Sevilla is the perfect location to call home. Our community offers large, open floorplans including some townhomes. In our homes you will find features such as: wood-like plank style flooring, full size washer/dryer connections, fireplaces and lots of closet space. These apartments were made with you in mind! Ample parking, a refreshing pool (open seasonally), and tons of walking trails nearby are just some of the things you have to look forward to while making Sevilla your home. Amenities Include: Carpeting (Select Units) Clubhouse Air Conditioner Electronic Thermostat Fireplace Patio/Balcony Refrigerator Microwave Near Public Transportation On-Site Maintenance On-Site Management Cable Ready Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/xj7r5xv2/sevilla-condos pricing and availability is subject to change daily.",
