        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 9450 Forest Springs Dr, Dallas, TX 75243 Charm, character and community in the beautiful Lake Highlands area of North Dallas. Our newly-renovated community is part of an exciting trend toward stylish change and revitalization in one of Dallas's most distinctive neighborhoods. The location is unparalleled, near four major highways and fantastic shopping, dining and entertainment. We have created affordable and beautifully designed, spacious interiors with access to multiple indoor and outdoor amenity spaces. Treat yourself to excellent living at affordable pricing! Apartment Features: Granite-Look Countertops Double Vanities Vaulted Ceilings Built in Bookcases Faux Wood Flooring Double Paned Windows Energy Efficient Appliances Ceiling Fan Brushed Nickel Hardware And Fixtures Washer and Dryer Connections Community Features: Laundry Facilities Public Transportation 24-Hour Security Surveillance & Monitoring Fitness Center Townhomes Pool Cabanas And Outdoor Kitchen On-Site Maintenance Playground Gated Community Controlled Access/Gated Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livevistapacific.com/5jjdnkos/link Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
