        "geocode_query": "15505 Hillcrest Rd",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Prestonwood 15505 Hillcrest Rd Dallas, TX 75248 Call or text us today at show contact info Apartment Information: 1 Bedroom | 1 Bath Apartment Size: 504 sq ft Monthly Price: $799 - $879 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Apartment Includes: ✓ Cable Ready ✓ Dishwasher ✓ High Speed Internet Access ✓ Refrigerator ✓ Electric Stoves ✓ Patio or Balcony ✓ Walk-in Closets Property Description: Our spacious one-, and two-bedroom apartment homes come complete with modern features like stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, hardwood-style flooring throughout, enhanced soundproofing for added privacy, and much more! With onsite management available 24/7 and an array of additional services including package acceptance and access to a car charging station, Prestonwood Apartments has everything you need to feel right at home. Come experience the elevated comfort and style that Prestonwood Apartments provides - you won't be disappointed! Schedule a tour: https://www.liveatprestonwood.com/?utm_knock=cl&doorway=schedule Property Amenities: ✓ Assigned Parking ✓ Covered Parking ✓ Laundry Facility ✓ Outdoor Grill ✓ Smoke Free ✓ Swimming Pool ✓ $299 1st month ✓ $99 1st month- selected units ✓ Free $255 App/admin Fee Special Look & Lease ✓ Picnic Area ✓ Swimming Pool Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=prestonwood&rp=iriZ9ABw8RSn&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=prestonwood&rp=iriZ9ABw8RSn&t=ap Call or text us today at show contact info Mon - Thu: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 4:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: Up to two pets per home no weight limit on dogs. A non-refundable pet fee of $175, refundable pet deposit of $175 and $25 monthly pet rent will be charged per pet under 50 lbs. All residents with animals are required to have PRIOR APPROVAL. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY EF5CEDEBEF6D4CE",
