        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post RENTAL INFO Monthly Price: $934 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Suncrest: 5444 Peterson Ln Dallas, TX 75240 Apartment for Rent: Studio-BR 1-BA | Square Feet: 540 sq ft | Lease Length: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Text or call to schedule a viewing: show contact info PROPERTY AMENITIES ✓ Charming Courtyard ✓ Close to I-635 ✓ Gated Community ✓ Laundry Facilities ✓ Pool ✓ Access to Love Field Airport ✓ Downtown Dallas is just a short drive away ✓ In the heart of Valley View Mall ✓ Pet Friendly Community APARTMENT AMENITIES ✓ Ceiling Fans ✓ Heating ✓ Pantry ✓ Patio/Balcony ✓ Walk-in Closets ✓ 1- or 2-bedroom options ✓ High-Speed Internet Access ✓ Smoke-free Patio/Balcony ✓ Washer & Dryer Hookups ADDITIONAL INFO Description: Welcome to Suncrest Apartment Homes, your new home in Dallas, Texas! When you choose Suncrest, you get the convenience of having all of your needs right at your fingertips. Located in the heart of Valley View Mall and close to I-635, downtown Dallas is just a short drive away. You'll also have easy access to Love Field Airport as well as hospitals and golf clubs located nearby. But if you prefer staying close to home, our gated community features an on-site pool for your enjoyment. Come experience the best that North Dallas has to offer when you make Suncrest Apartment Homes your home today! Our pet-friendly community features thoughtfully designed amenities, smoke-free balconies and a variety of studio, 1-bedroom and 2-bedroom apartment homes. Add in our charming courtyard and convenient central location, and you have all the advantages of modern city living without sacrificing comfort or quality. Come experience Suncrest today - we can't wait to welcome you home! Schedule a tour: https://www.liveatsuncrest.com/?utm_knock=cl&doorway=schedule Pet Policy: Animal Limitations: Up to two pets per home no weight limit on dogs. A non-refundable pet fee of $200, refundable pet deposit of $200 and $35 monthly pet rent will be charged per pet under 50 lbs. All residents with animals are required to have PRIOR APPROVAL. Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=suncrest&rp=gUxnfLKLYtkX&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=suncrest&rp=gUxnfLKLYtkX&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=suncrest&rp=gUxnfLKLYtkX&t=sch Text or call to schedule a viewing: show contact info All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 70D78060D7E647C",
