        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Suncrest 5444 Peterson Ln Dallas, TX 75240 Drop us a call or text at show contact info Apartment Information: 2 Bedroom | 2 Bath Apartment Size: 1012 sq ft Monthly Price: $1455 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month Apartment Includes: − Ceiling Fans − Heating − Pantry − Patio/Balcony − Walk-in Closets − 1- or 2-bedroom options − High-Speed Internet Access − Smoke-free Patio/Balcony − Washer & Dryer Hookups Property Description: Located near the heart of Dallas, you'll have an International Airport, Shopping, Golf Courses, and Major Freeway Access in minutes. Our pet-friendly community features thoughtfully designed amenities, smoke-free balconies and a variety of studio, 1-bedroom and 2-bedroom apartment homes. Add in our charming courtyard and convenient central location, and you have all the advantages of modern city living without sacrificing comfort or quality. Come experience Suncrest today - we can't wait to welcome you home! Property Amenities: − Charming Courtyard − Close to I-635 − Gated Community − Laundry Facilities − Pool − Access to Love Field Airport − Downtown Dallas is just a short drive away − In the heart of Valley View Mall − Pet Friendly Community Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=suncrest&rp=wuFXqAGACsn5&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=suncrest&rp=wuFXqAGACsn5&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=suncrest&rp=wuFXqAGACsn5&t=sch Drop us a call or text at show contact info Mon - Thu: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Fri: 9:00 AM - 4:00 PM Pet Ownership Policy: Animal Limitations: Up to two pets per home no weight limit on dogs. A non-refundable pet fee of $200, refundable pet deposit of $200 and $35 monthly pet rent will be charged per pet under 50 lbs. All residents with animals are required to have PRIOR APPROVAL. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 1F05BEF3C16B4968",
