        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Metropolitan at Cityplace Monthly Price: $2435 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 1207 sq ft BEDROOMS: 3 BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Text or call to schedule a viewing: show contact info APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: ✓ Carpet ✓ Ceiling Fans ✓ Dishwasher & Disposal ✓ High Speed Internet And Cable Ready ✓ Ice Maker ✓ Individual Locking Bedrooms ✓ Microwave ✓ Refrigerator/Freezer ✓ Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms) ✓ Window Coverings ✓ Covered Balcony W/ Outside Storage! ✓ Eat-in Kitchen ✓ Framed Mirror Accents in Dining & Bath ✓ Hardwood Style Flooring ✓ Instant Hot Water ✓ In-Unit Washers & Dryers ✓ Large Bedrooms ✓ Stainless Steel Appliances In Select Apt ✓ Vaulted Ceiling ✓ Warming Drawer Our community is designed to serve your needs with our 24-hour fitness center, pool, business center and more. Enjoy the peace of mind knowing that there is controlled access throughout our gated property for added courtesy officers. We are also pet-friendly with green spaces for them to explore plus in-home upgrades that come standard with every unit - including all appliances and fixtures. Schedule a tour: https://www.metropolitancityplace.com/?utm_knock=cl&doorway=schedule PROPERTY FEATURES: ✓ Clubhouse ✓ Controlled Access ✓ Courtyard ✓ Fenced Lot ✓ Fitness Center ✓ Grill & Picnic Area ✓ Lawn ✓ Package Service ✓ Renters Insurance Program ✓ Trash Pickup - Door to Door ✓ Fire Pit Station ✓ Green Community ✓ Online Services ✓ Pet-Friendly Green Spaces ✓ Planned Social Activities ✓ Resort-Style Pool ✓ Study Lounge ✓ Video Patrol ✓ Views ✓ Wifi in Common Spaces PET POLICY: Up to two pets per home no weight limit on dogs. A non-refundable pet fee of $300, refundable pet deposit of $200 and $20 monthly pet rent will be charged per pet. All residents with animals are required to have PRIOR APPROVAL. VISIT