        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Fairfax Monthly Price: $970 - $1060 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. SIZE: 734 sq ft BEDROOMS: 1 BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: 6-Month, 12-Month Call or text us: show contact info APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: ➢ Carpet ➢ Dining Room ➢ High Speed Internet Access ➢ Patio ➢ Built in Desk in Select Units ➢ Washer/Dryer ➢ Wood-Style Vintage Flooring As one of Dallas's finest apartment communities, Fairfax offers residents a life of luxury through our many distinct offerings. Fairfax apartments have something to contribute to any lifestyle desired. With easy access to Downtown Dallas and DFW International Airport, Fairfax apartments reside in the most convenient of locations. Schedule a tour: https://liveatfairfaxapts.com/?utm_knock=cl&doorway=schedule PROPERTY FEATURES: ➢ Controlled Access Gated Community ➢ Fenced Lot ➢ On-Site Laundry Facility ➢ Smoke Free ➢ Bark Park ➢ Courtyard with Green Spaces ➢ Covered Parking Available ➢ Sparkling Swimming Pool PET POLICY: Up to two pets per home no weight limit on dogs. A non-refundable pet fee of $150, refundable pet deposit of $150 and $20 monthly pet rent will be charged per pet. All residents with animals are required to have PRIOR APPROVAL. VISIT US TODAY! 6201 Bordeaux Ave Dallas, TX 75209 Call or text us: show contact info Website: www.rentalsapts.com?n=fairfax&rp=qw8pK2Z2qhba&t=wb Online Application: www.rentalsapts.com?n=fairfax&rp=qw8pK2Z2qhba&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY B2C65297E3EC47AF",
