        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Briella Fort Worth Rental Information Base monthly rent: $900 - $1384 Mandatory monthly fees: $26.50 Total Monthly Price: $926.50 - $1410.50 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. 1 Bedroom 1 Bath | 748 sq ft Lease Term: Variable Call: show contact info One Month Free + WIN FREE RENT FOR ONE YEAR! $99 Administrative and application fee! One month free! Lease today! *Restrictions Apply, Contact for Details Free Rent, Unlocked: Lease by Aug. 5 for a chance to win free rent for one year. No purchase necessary. See official rules at rpmsummersweeps.com. Apartment Amenities ✓ Cable Ready ✓ Ceiling Fans ✓ Dishwasher ✓ Disposal ✓ Fireplace/ In Select Units ✓ Heating ✓ Microwave/ In Select Units ✓ Refrigerator ✓ Tub/Shower ✓ Vinyl Flooring/ Carpet ✓ 1 Bedroom Full Reno ✓ 2 Bedroom Full Reno ✓ Air Conditioning ✓ Contemporary Finishes ✓ High Speed Internet Access ✓ Quartz Countertops/ In Select Units ✓ Upgraded Lighting/ In Select Units ✓ Washer and Dryer in Home / In Select Units ✓ Window Coverings ✓ Wood-Style Flooring/ In Select Units Community Features ✓ Carport(s) ✓ Community Laundry Room ✓ Grill Station ✓ On-Site Maintenance ✓ Playground ✓ Property Manager on Site ✓ Soccer Field ✓ Sparkling Swimming Pool About Community Description: Embark on a visual journey of Briella Fort Worth Apartments and immerse yourself in the essence of your potential new home. Our photos are a window into the world of modern comfort, style, and convenience that awaits you here. Explore our photo gallery today and start envisioning your life in this exceptional space - your new home at Briella Fort Worth Apartments. Location: 6011 Oakland Hills Dr Fort Worth, TX 76112 show contact info Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Additional Information Call: show contact info Pet Policy: At RPM Living, we feel your pets are members of our extended family, so we strive to make them feel right at home. Briella Fort Worth Apartments welcomes cats and dogs with no breed restrictions. For each pet, with a maximum of two - there is a non-refundable pet fee of $400 and pet rent of $30 per month. Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=briella_fort_worth&rp=6Dz2gczVnN26&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=briella_fort_worth&rp=6Dz2gczVnN26&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 314D3B73768C4E29",
