        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Tides on Larga Base monthly rent: $649 - $983 Mandatory monthly fees: $30.50 Total Monthly Price: $679.50 - $1013.50 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. SIZE: 528 sq ft BEDROOMS: 1 BATHROOMS: 1 LEASE TERMS: Call Call us today! show contact info APARTMENT HOME FEATURES: ◾ Balcony ◾ Ceiling Fans ◾ Dishwasher ◾ Fireplace ◾ Heating ◾ Kitchen ◾ Microwave ◾ Patio ◾ Range ◾ Refrigerator ◾ 1 Bedroom Full Reno ◾ Air Conditioning ◾ Contemporary Finishes ◾ Framed Mirrors ◾ Hardwood Floors ◾ High Speed Internet Access ◾ Prior Upgrade ◾ Upgraded Lighting ◾ Vinyl Flooring ◾ Walk-In Closets Explore the options with our selection of six spacious one and two-bedroom apartment homes in Dallas, Texas, at Tides on Larga. Experience modern living with contemporary finishes, upgraded lighting, wood-style flooring, and an in-home washer and dryer. . Prepare a gourmet meal in your well-equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances, including a microwave, a refrigerator, a dishwasher, and quartz countertops. At Tides on Larga, we're a pet-friendly community, welcoming your entire family to experience the best in comfortable living. PROPERTY FEATURES: ◾ 24 Hour Access ◾ Courtyard ◾ Gated ◾ Laundry Facilities ◾ Maintenance on site ◾ Online Services ◾ Playground ◾ Property Manager on Site ◾ Storage Space ◾ Sundeck ◾ Beautiful Landscaping ◾ Guest Parking ◾ High-speed Internet Access Available ◾ Picnic Area with Barbecue ◾ Play Area ◾ Shimmering Swimming Pool ◾ Spanish Speaking Staff ◾ Sports Court PET POLICY: At RPM Living, we feel your pets are members of our extended family, so we strive to make them feel right at home. Tides on Larga welcomes cats and dogs, with a maximum of two. Contact our leasing office for more information! VISIT US TODAY! 3330 Webb Chapel Ext Dallas, TX 75220 Call us today! show contact info Website: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=tides_on_larga&rp=61nmvMzFKQpK&t=wb Online Application: www.leaseaptsnow.com?n=tides_on_larga&rp=61nmvMzFKQpK&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY IJR3BSKB1D3N0MX",
