        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Tides on Larga Visit our community today! 3330 Webb Chapel Ext Dallas, TX 75220 Call us at show contact info Base monthly rent: $848 - $1054 Mandatory monthly fees: $30.50 Total Monthly Price: $878.50 - $1084.50 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Apartment Type: 1-BR 1-BA Apartment Size: 558 sq ft Lease Terms: Call Pet Policy: At RPM Living, we feel your pets are members of our extended family, so we strive to make them feel right at home. Tides on Larga welcomes cats and dogs, with a maximum of two. Contact our leasing office for more information! What you'll find in our community: ➢ Courtyard ➢ Gated ➢ Laundry Facilities ➢ Maintenance on site ➢ Online Services ➢ Playground ➢ Property Manager on Site ➢ Storage Space ➢ Sundeck ➢ Walk-Up ➢ Beautiful Landscaping ➢ Guest Parking ➢ High-speed Internet Access Available ➢ Picnic Area with Barbecue ➢ Play Area ➢ Shimmering Swimming Pool ➢ Spanish Speaking Staff ➢ Sports Court Description: Strategically positioned near TX-12 and Interstate 35 E, Tides on Larga is your entry point to Dallas, Texas's vibrant and thrilling experiences. Our pet-friendly community is mere miles from the city center, enveloped by a wealth of entertainment options, delectable dining establishments, and captivating shops, ensuring abundant activities in the vicinity. This apartment comes with: ➢ Ceiling Fans ➢ Fireplace ➢ Heating ➢ Kitchen ➢ Microwave ➢ Oven ➢ Patio ➢ Range ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Tub/Shower ➢ Air Conditioning ➢ Framed Mirrors ➢ Hardwood Floors ➢ High Speed Internet Access ➢ Prior Upgrade ➢ Quartz Countertops ➢ Stainless Steel Appliances ➢ Upgraded Lighting ➢ Vinyl Flooring ➢ Window Coverings Call us at show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM Visit our website to schedule a personal tour! Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=tides_on_larga&rp=s5uMkE5QLgrs&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=tides_on_larga&rp=s5uMkE5QLgrs&t=ap All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 7ON4CAK7JJH0RAT",
