        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Reserve at Spring Creek Contact Info: show contact info 1 month FREE when you move in by 7/31/26 on a 12+ month term!* *RESTRICTIONS APPLY. CONTACT US FOR DETAILS. Apartment Details: 2-BR 2-BA | Square Footage: 1328 sq ft Monthly Price: $2138 - $2525 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Length: Call Apartment Features: ➢ ADA ➢ Air conditioning ➢ Ceiling Fan ➢ Dishwasher ➢ Disposal ➢ Heating ➢ Microwave ➢ Refrigerator ➢ Roof terrace ➢ Tub/shower ➢ Eat-in kitchen ➢ Framed mirrors ➢ High speed internet access ➢ Historic Cemetery View ➢ Patio/Balcony ➢ Private Rooftop Decks* ➢ Private Yards ➢ Vinyl flooring ➢ W/D Hookup ➢ Wheelchair Access About Our Community: At Reserve at Spring Creek, we offer a variety of spacious floor plans designed to fit your unique lifestyle. Whether you're looking for a cozy one-bedroom for a professional or a larger two-bedroom for a growing family, our luxury apartments in Richardson, TX, are thoughtfully crafted with modern features and high-end finishes to enhance your living experience. Our apartments are designed with both comfort and functionality in mind. Each layout includes smart-home features, large living spaces, and premium finishes that make coming home a pleasure. Enjoy the convenience of spacious closets, modern kitchens, and open-concept living areas that provide the perfect space for relaxation and entertaining. Plus, with pet-friendly options available, your furry friends are always welcome. Pet Policy: We welcome you and your pet home to an MG Properties community. Before you move in, we ask that you review our pet policy. Wonderful Amenities: ➢ BBQ/Picnic Area ➢ Billiard Table ➢ Clubhouse ➢ Courtyard ➢ Elevator ➢ Lounge ➢ Pet Friendly ➢ Pet play area ➢ Storage space ➢ Business Center ➢ Car charging station ➢ Controlled Access/Gated ➢ Craft Beer Garden ➢ Direct Access to Spring Creek Nature Preserve ➢ Gameroom ➢ Key fob entry ➢ On-Site Maintenance ➢ On-Site Management ➢ Resort-Inspired Pool Contact Information: Address: 2710 Routh Creek Pkwy Richardson, TX 75082 Contact Info: show contact info Website: www.apt-rental.com?n=reserve_at_spring_creek&rp=rrVcWicQzEjK&t=wb Online Application: www.apt-rental.com?n=reserve_at_spring_creek&rp=rrVcWicQzEjK&t=ap 3D Virtual Tour: www.apt-rental.com?n=reserve_at_spring_creek&rp=rrVcWicQzEjK&t=trt All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY ECS7S34G770749B4",
